{"tid":149268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日笑話]中國發人權紀錄 批美不顧自身問題","createTime":"2017-03-09T07:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T16:46:59.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a308b91b693455c0e493f5e1e7b15b8d8bdaf5c0","tid":149268,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"國務院新聞辦公室發布《2016年美國的人權紀錄》及《2016年美國侵犯人權事記》，回應美國國務院此前所發布的《國別人權報告》，批評美國對世界各國人權狀況品頭論足、橫加指責，但對其自身存在的嚴重人權問題全然不顧。<br />\n<br />\n中國所發布的《人權紀錄》指出，美國涉槍犯罪持續高發，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>監禁率居高不下</strong></span>，去年全年共發生槍擊事件5.81萬宗，共造成1.5萬人死亡，亦提及美國監禁率居世界第二。<br />\n<br />\n該《紀錄》認為，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>美國警察濫用執法權力、選舉政治權利無法保障、中低收入群體生活狀況堪憂</strong></span>，又批評美國種族主義持續存在，種族關係日趨惡化。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國新辦的《美國侵犯人權事記》則記錄了去年全年在美國發生的侵犯人權事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1508763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1508763&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41FeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=8d494c44\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1508763</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dc2206144b5691e2cb262b6eda7b0edc96668e","tid":149268,"uid":87506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"事實來<br />\n你估美國警察無濫用私刑？<br />\n無歧視黑人？"},{"pid":"fe9509d4187cef88aadb39939dba371caa7f78e2","tid":149268,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實來<br />\n你估美國警察無濫用私刑？<br />\n無歧視黑人？</blockquote><br />\n10000億步笑50步"},{"pid":"bac70cb1e32a90f5884fc437fe7a70ae50c35292","tid":149268,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實來<br />\n你估美國警察無濫用私刑？<br />\n無歧視黑人？</blockquote><br />\n10000億步笑50步</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo